                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Denby</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Sherman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Peking, China</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-04-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 20, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 2917.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that Kwangchau
                    Bay, which has been recently ceded to the French Government for ninety-nine
                    years, is situate on the southwestern coast of China, in the district of
                    Leichou, Kwangtung Province.</p>
                <p>The harbor is said to be a good one. The country back of it is highly productive.
                    One of the chief products is sugar.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Charles Denby.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
